        <briefdescription>
<para>Values for <ref refid="group__sensor__interface_1gga0dcb6842bc969492bd1c9eb49708940bacb07e3508ea5503dbcdceee3f17d2291" kindref="member">SENSOR_ATTR_SAMPLING_FREQUENCY</ref> (Hz) </para>
